@title InterestConnector
 @dev This contract gives an abstract way of receiving interest on locked tokens.

attributes.text:
@title InterestConnector
 @dev This contract gives an abstract way of receiving interest on locked tokens.

devdoc.details: This contract gives an abstract way of receiving interest on locked tokens.

disableInterest(address).details: Disables interest for locked funds. Only owner can call this method. Prior to calling this function, consider to call payInterest and claimCompAndPay.

params._token: of token to disable interest for.

initializeInterest(address,address,uint2.details: Initializes interest receiving functionality for the particular locked token. Only owner can call this method.

params._impl: address of the interest earning implementation contract.
params._minCashThreshold: minimum amount of underlying tokens that are not invested.
params._token: address of the token for interest earning.

interestImplementation(address).details: Tells address of the interest earning implementation for the specific token contract. If interest earning is disabled, will return 0x00..00. Can be an address of the deployed CompoundInterestERC20 contract.

params._token: address of the locked token contract.

invest(address).details: Invests all excess tokens. Leaves only minCashThreshold in underlying tokens. Requires interest for the given token to be enabled first.

params._token: address of the token contract considered.

mediatorBalance(address).details: Tells the expected token balance of the contract.

returns._0: the current tracked token balance of the contract.

minCashThreshold(address).details: Tells minimum amount of tokens that are not being invested.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

owner().details: Tells the address of the owner

setMinCashThreshold(address,uint256).details: Sets minimum amount of tokens that cannot be invested. Only owner can call this method.

params._minCashThreshold: minimum amount of underlying tokens that are not invested.

transferOwnership(address).details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.

params.newOwner: the address to transfer ownership to.
